Package com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.ui.components

Custom UI components used in VisualVM.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataViewComponent
    UI component displaying single subtab for opened DataSource.
    DataViewComponent.DetailsAreaConfiguration
    Configuration for details area.
    DataViewComponent.DetailsView
    Details view of DataViewComponent.
    DataViewComponent.DetailsViewConfiguration
    Configuration of the DetailsView.
    DataViewComponent.MasterView
    Master view of DataViewComponent.
    DataViewComponent.MasterViewConfiguration
    Configuration of the MasterView.
    LevelIndicator
    Graphical component for fall-off level indicator
    NotSupportedDisplayer
    JPanel showing a predefined message.
    ScrollableContainer
    Predefined JScrollPane to be used in VisualVM, for example in details views.
    SectionSeparator
    Separator-like component to be used instead of TitledBorder to keep the UI lightweight.
    Spacer
    Subclass of a JPanel to be used as a spacer in GridBagLayout.
